40:34.693 --> 40:37.130
♪ Ooh... ♪

40:38.174 --> 40:40.263
♪ I want to feel it ♪

40:40.307 --> 40:43.615
♪ Feel it, feel it ♪

40:43.658 --> 40:46.531
♪ Feel it coming home ♪

