NANCY:
Karendid know Lucy.

41:23.132 --> 41:25.744
Why'd she lie?

41:25.787 --> 41:27.789
♪ Feel it coming home ♪

41:29.487 --> 41:31.663
[entry bell jingles]

41:31.706 --> 41:34.448
♪ Feel it coming home ♪

41:37.712 --> 41:40.062
♪ Feel it coming home... ♪

